_sText:
Story:
The Counter-Terrorists have tracked down
a group of Terrorists who are raiding 
a secret area in the middle of Egypt.
The Terrorists have no choice but to
evacuate but wont leave without blowing
the base to pieces first.

Authors note:
I created the map due to a few of my favorite
servers using zm_lila_panic as a fightyard map.
I really hated the poor quality of the map so made
a version which had same gameplay but also looked
decent. I did add 1 new route but it was just to balance
the gameplay out. The new route gives the Terrorist
team a 60% better chance of survival, the other route
is from the original layout and was always the rush point
for the Counter-Terrorists team. Also i spent a long time
on optimizing the map so it will output around the same fps.

Other notes:
64 Spawn points|32 each team.
1 Main bombsite.
Nav inside the bsp.
Protected from Decompile.
